\fICT_DIRECTION\fR := \fB"original"\fR | \fB"reply"\fR
.fi
.if n \{\
.RE
.\}
.sp
Create a reference to packet conntrack data\&.
.sp
Some CT keys do not support a direction\&. In this case, \fBdir\fR must not be given\&.
.SS "NUMGEN"
.sp
.if n \{\
.RS 4
.\}
.nf
\fB{ "numgen": {
